{"id": 59420, "date": "2025-08-24T04:00:23", "date_gmt": "2025-08-24T11:00:23", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59420"}, "modified": "2026-06-01T15:39:39", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-01T22:39:39", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-august-24-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/24/kingdom-of-days-august-24-2/", "title": {"rendered": "August 24"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1968:\u00a0</strong>Earth plays a private gig at a wedding in Brooklyn.</p>\n<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their fifth night of a week-long residency at Oliver&#8217;s in Boston.</p>\n<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>A scheduled show is cancelled at the Cinematic Circus in Woodbourne, New York.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"12310\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-08-24/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-24.jpg?fit=151%2C499&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"151,499\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-08-24\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-24.jpg?fit=151%2C499&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12310 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-24.jpg?resize=151%2C499&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"151\" height=\"499\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-24.jpg?w=151&amp;ssl=1 151w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1974-08-24.jpg?resize=91%2C300&amp;ssl=1 91w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 151px) 100vw, 151px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band hold a recording session in New York City for their upcoming album.</p>\n<p><strong>1979:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the band record &#8220;Point Blank&#8221; and an early arrangement of &#8220;You Can Look (Buy You Better Not Touch)&#8221; during a recording session at the Power Station in New York City.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/69Gz0eCDtXs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>At the fourth night of a six-night River Tour stand at the L.A. Sports Arena, Tom Waits makes a guest appearance for (what else?) &#8220;Jersey Girl.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1MXX0Y81eDI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EL0CFhgBhz8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"54154\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/simi_valley_star_1981_08_26_34/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Simi_Valley_Star_1981_08_26_34.jpg?fit=2422%2C886&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2422,886\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Simi_Valley_Star_1981_08_26_34\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Simi_Valley_Star_1981_08_26_34.jpg?fit=758%2C278&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-54154 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Simi_Valley_Star_1981_08_26_34.jpg?resize=758%2C277&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"277\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Simi_Valley_Star_1981_08_26_34.jpg?w=2422&amp;ssl=1 2422w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Simi_Valley_Star_1981_08_26_34.jpg?resize=300%2C110&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/u